      "text": "Teem buhs tam KUN-\nGAM pateikt par winna Scheh-\nastibu/ un par winna Brihnu-\nneem/ pee Zilweka Behrneem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ka winch falansch War-\na Durwis/ un tadausa Dselsu\nKinkus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tee/ kas Gekki tappu-\nchi zaur winnu Pahrkahpscha-\nas Zelfu/ un fatvu Noseegumu\necht mohziti tappe.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta ka winnu Dwehfelei\nreefsch wiffas Barrihas ree-\nahs/ un nogrimme lihds patt\nNahwes Wahrtim.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Rad tee to KUNGII\nveefauze eeksch jawahm Beh-\nahm/ un winch tohs isglahbe\nio winnu Isbailehm.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Wiꞥſch fuhtija fawn\nWahrdn/ un dseedinaja tohs/ un\nsrahwe tohs no winnu Bed-\nehm.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Teem buhs tam KUN-\nGAM pateikt par winna Scheh-\nastibu/ un par winna Brihnu-\nneem/ pee Zilweka Behrneem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Pateikschanas-Uppu-\nus uppureht/ un winna Dar-\nus isteikt ar Preeku.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tee kas ar leelahm Lai-\nvahm us Juhru lihgojahs/ un\nosinne fawn Darbu us leelem\nihdenim.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kas ta KUNGA Darbu\nedsejschi/un winna Brihnunus\neeksch Dsittumeem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Rad tasrunnaja/ un wee-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ka tee itt ka us Debbesim\nkahpe/ un attak Dsittumos no-\ngrimme/ ka winnu Dwehtele no\nBailibas iskuffe.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ka tee lehze un mehtati\ntappe/ ka weens Beedsehris/ un\nwiffa winnu Gudriba isnihke.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 28,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tee to KUNGU pee-\nfauze eeksch jawahm Behdahm/\nun winch tohs isglahbe no win-\nnu Isbailehm.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 29,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Winch kluftinaja to Weh-\ntru / ta ka winnas Wilni no-\nrimme.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 30,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tee preezajahs ka rahms\ntappis/ un winch tohs us to\nOhstu pawaddijs/kas teem grib-\nbejahs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 31,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Teem buhs tam KUN-\nGAM pateikt par winna Scheh-\nastibu/ un par winna Brihnu-\nneeni/ pee Zilweka Behrneem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 32,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un winnu pa-augstinaht\neeksch to Lanschn Draudsibas/\nun pee teem Wezzajeem winnu\nflaweht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 33,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Rad winch Uppes par\nTuksnibu padarra/ un uhdens\nAwoschus par iskaltuschahm\nWeetahm.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 34,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un anglin Semmi par\nne-anglinu padarra / winnas\nEedschwotaju Blehdibas deht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 35,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un winch attak to Tuks-\nnibu uhdenaizu padarrija/ un\ntausu Semmi awoffnaizu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 36,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un leek tur tohs Isfal-\nkuschus dshwoht / ka tee Pills-\n"
    }
  ],
